				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/C%E1%BA%A5p-giang-ti%C3%AAn-tr%C3%A0/poem-q8346Hj_4cF4MP4KzsKlew">Cấp giang tiên trà - 汲江煎茶</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/author-ZsPeAEZWTH-jxxg2cYfLgg">Tô Thức</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Nguy%C3%AAn-%C4%90%C3%A1n/Ch%C3%ADnh-T%C3%BAc-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-gia-y%E1%BA%BFn-t%E1%BB%8Bch-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-ph%C3%BA-mai-thi-th%E1%BB%A9-Gi%E1%BB%9Bi-Hi%C3%AAn-b%E1%BB%99c-x%E1%BA%A1-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-WCb_4bzmiU3bev6NftcAAA">Chính Túc Vương gia yến tịch thượng, phú mai thi thứ Giới Hiên bộc xạ vận - 正肅王家宴席上賦梅詩次介軒僕射韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Nguy%C3%AAn-%C4%90%C3%A1n/author-h_HbFCmxWKkwxboqzaEfNA">Trần Nguyên Đán</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Th%C3%A1nh-T%C3%B4ng/%C4%90%C3%A0-giang-ti%E1%BB%83u-b%E1%BA%A1c/poem-2laMSMpbP5tPcv6xVG43pg">Đà giang tiểu bạc - 陀江小泊</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Th%C3%A1nh-T%C3%B4ng/author-FSJg5-ivZkPUR1nhJkA6Fg">Lê Thánh Tông</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A2n-Kh%C3%AD-T%E1%BA%ADt/Gi%C3%A1-c%C3%B4-thi%C3%AAn-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1i-nh%C3%A2n-ph%C3%BA-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-U2g-209n7RhRIvXow_ponQ">Giá cô thiên - Đại nhân phú kỳ 2 - 鷓鴣天－代人賦其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A2n-Kh%C3%AD-T%E1%BA%ADt/author-cR0yq4BrF6xGIKZCvJGLSA">Tân Khí Tật</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BA%A5u-Chu%E1%BA%A9n/Giang-Nam-xu%C3%A2n/poem-qx4Mf8NxOHIO49l_GfxTgQ">Giang Nam xuân - 江南春</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BA%A5u-Chu%E1%BA%A9n/author-5Cf60ts6PJnoMBTjftHTrg">Khấu Chuẩn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ti%E1%BA%BFt-%E1%BB%90t/T%E1%BA%B7ng-c%E1%BB%91-nh%C3%A2n/poem-acPxU5xDVty6a7yOK2AVQQ">Tặng cố nhân - 贈故人</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ti%E1%BA%BFt-%E1%BB%90t/author-BRLX5z128FjcCRokBpNHAw">Tiết Ốt</a